 and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"damonN","text_ar":"دَمْنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adamaAnN","text_ar":"اَدَمَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ibn-Abi-z-Zinád, T, IKtt, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rottenness and blackness of a palm-tree:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state of a palm-tree"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*aA A^anosagato","text_ar":"اـِذَا اَنْسَغَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as As says, (T, S, [and the like is said in the M,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano tunosiga Aln~axolapu","text_ar":"اَنْ تُنْسِغَ النَّخْلَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) but Sh says, correctly,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*aA","text_ar":"اـِذَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@no$aq~ato","text_ar":"ا@نْشَقَّتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when it splits"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in consequence of rottenness and blackness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M:) or, accord. to IAth,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corruptness and rottenness of fruits"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alvmr","text_ar":"الثمر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[perhaps a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~amor","text_ar":"التَّمْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dates"},{"kind":"text","text":"])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before their coming to maturity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"damaAlN","text_ar":"دَمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"damaAnN","text_ar":"دَمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"damaAlN","text_ar":"دَمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"both signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an unsoundness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"infection, in the spadix of the palm-tree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dml","text_ar":"دمل"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that it becomes black,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA ib.,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before it attains to maturity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh and TA ib.,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before it is fecundated."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA ib.)       -A3-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"damaAnN","text_ar":"دَمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) or in this sense it is correctly ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dam~aAnN","text_ar":"دَمَّانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who manures land with"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the dung called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siroqiyn","text_ar":"سِرْقِين"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K, * TA.)       -A4-  [Golius adds the signification of “ Tormentum, supplicium, ” as from the KL, in my copy of which the only explanation given is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EfwntY kh bh drxt xrmA rsd","text_ar":"عفونتى كه به درخت خرما رسد"},{"kind":"text","text":"“ a rottenness that infects a palm-tree: ” he seems to have found in his copy of that work"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EqwbtY","text_ar":"عقوبتى"},{"kind":"text","text":", either alone, or followed by some words imperfectly written.]"}],"source_refs":["M","K","TA","As","Sh","T","S","IAth"]},{"entry_id":"n13147","headword_ar":"دُمَانٌ","root":"dmn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dimaAnN","text_ar":"دِمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n13148","headword_ar":"دَمَّانٌ","root":"dmn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"damaAnN","text_ar":"دَمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}